課程概述 Course Description
          History	 Scanning	 robe	 Microscopy
	 
n��   Nobel	 Prize,	 STM,	 AFM,	 commercialization
	 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    Topics:

History of Scanning Probe Microscopy
	
Nobel Prize, STM, AFM, commercialization


Operation Principles
Tip-Sample Interactions
Derivatives of SPM
	
Various scanning modes
Different operation principles
New applications


Case/Paper Study and Discussion



